data.description: Welcome to this 2 story 4 BR 2.5 Bath home in the Lakeshore Subdivision.  This home has been updated and now the Main level features Hardwood floors in the formal Dining and Living. The kitchen has updated Stainless Steel Appliances,  Granite-Tops, Breakfast Bar/ room with Tiled Floors. The 2nd floor features 4 Bedrooms including a Master suite with Garden Tub and Shower.  This home is located near end of the cul-de-sac and features  breath-taking views of the lake. Hurry up and bring your buyers and offers!!!
